<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
<data>
<template id="hr_payroll_fdfp_report">
    <t t-call="report.html_container">
        <t t-set="data_report_margin_top" t-value="5"/>
        <t t-set="data_report_margin_left" t-value="5"/>
        <t t-set="data_report_margin_rigth" t-value="5"/>
        <t t-set="data_report_header_spacing" t-value="5"/>
        <t t-set="data_report_dpi" t-value="110"/>

        <t t-foreach="docs" t-as="o">
            <div class="page">
                <style type="text/css">
                    .tb1{ width: 100%;}
                    .tb1d0{ width: 20%; border: 0.5px solid black; font: 12px bold 'Arial';}
                    .tb1d1{ width: 60%; border: 0.5px solid black; font: 14px bold 'Arial'; border-top: none; border-bottom: none;}
                    .tb1d2 { width: 20%; border: 0.5px solid black; ;}
                    .h0 { margin-top: 10px;}
                    .tb0{ width: 100%; font: 11px 'Arial';}
                    .tb0r0d0{ width: 20%; font: 10px 'Arial';}
                    .tb0r0d1{ width: 3%;}
                    .tb0r0d2{ width: 4%; border: 0.5px solid black; background-color: rgba(240, 255, 167, 1);
                        border-top: none;font: bold 15px 'Arial'; text-align: right; padding: 0px 2px;}
                    .tb0r0d4 { text-align: center; border: 0.5px solib white; }
                    .tb0r0d5{  border-bottom: 0.5px; border-style: dotted; width: 20%;}
                    .title{ margin-top: 5px; margin-left: 5px; font: bold 16px 'Arial';}
                    .t0{ font: bold 10px 'Arial'; width: 100%; text-align: center;}
                    .t0d0{ border: 0.5px solid black; width: 12%;}
                    .t0d1{ border: none; width: 5%; }
                    .t0d2{ border: 0.5px solid black;}
                    .t0d3{ border: 0.5px solid black;}
                    .t0d4{ border: 0.5px solid black; background-color: rgba(240, 255, 167, 1);}
                    .t1{ font: bold 10px 'Arial'; width: 100%; text-align: center;}
                    .t1r0 { text-align: center; padding: 5px 5px;}
                    .t1r0d0{ border: 0.5px solid black; width: 35%;}
                    .t1r0d1{ border: 0.5px solid black; width: 10%;}
                    .t1r0d2{ border: 0.5px solid black; }
                    .t1r1d0{ text-align: left; border: 0.5px solid black; padding-left: 5px;}
                    .t1r1d1{ background-color: rgba(240, 255, 167, 1); border: 0.5px solid black;}
                    .t1r1d3{ border: 0.5px solid black;}
                    .d2{ margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;}
                    .t2 { width: 100%}
                    .t2r0d0 { width: 75% }
                    .t2r0d1 { width: 30%; border: 0.5px solid black; background-color: rgba(240, 255, 167, 1);}
                    .t2r0d2 { width: 5%; }
                    .t3{ width: 100%}
                    .t3r0d{ width: 70%; border: 0.5px solid black; }
                    .t3r0d0{ width: 30%; border: 0.5px solid black; border-bottom: none; text-align: center; }
                    .t3r0d1 { width: 70%; border: 0.5px solid black; text-align: left; border-top: none; padding-left: 5px;}
                    .t3r0d2 { border: 0.5px solid black; text-align: center;}
                    .t3r0d4 { background-color:rgba(240, 255, 167, 1);}
                    .t3r0d5{ height: 50px; border: none}
                    .footer{ margin-top: 50px; font: 12px 'Arial'; width: 100%; text-align: left;}
                </style>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12">
                        <div class="col-xs-3">NCC : <span t-field="user.company_id.num_contribuable"/></div>
                        <div class="col-xs-6 text-center">
                            REPUBLIQUE DE COTE D'IVOIRE<br/>
                                Union-Discipline-Travail<br/>
                            -------------------------<br/>
                           MINISTERE AUPRES DU PREMIER MINISTRE,<br/>
                                    CHARGE DU BUDGET<br/>
                            -------------------------
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="h1">
                    <table class="tb1">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="tb1d0">CACHET DU SERVICE</td>
                            <td class="tb1d1" rowspan="2">
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <strong>DIRECTION GENERALE DES IMPOTS</strong><br/>
                                <img src="hr_payroll_ci_raport/static/img/dgi2.jpg"
                                     style="max-height: 30px;
                                     width: 100px;
                                    display: block;
                                    margin-left: auto;
                                    margin-right: auto;
                                    padding:auto;"
                                />
                                    <strong>TAXE D'APPRENTISSAGE ET TAXE</strong><br/>
                                <strong>ADDITIONNELLE A LA FORMATION CONTINUE</strong><br/>
                                    (Articles 143 et suivants du CGI)<br/>
                                    --------------------------------<br/>

                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="tb1d0">DATE DE RECEPTION</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="tb1d2" ></td>
                            <td class="tb1d2" ></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td></td>
                            <td align="center" style="font: 12px bold 'Arial';"><strong>ETAT ANNEXE</strong></td>
                            <td></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <div class="h0">
                    <table class="tb0">
                        <tr>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d0"><sup>PERIODE D'IMPOSITION</sup></td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d1"></td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2"><span t-esc="data['month_1']"/></td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2"><span t-esc="data['month_2']"/></td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d1"></td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2">0</td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2"><span t-esc="data['quarter']"/></td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d1"></td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2"><span t-esc="data['year_1']"/></td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d2"><span t-esc="data['year_2']"/></td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d1"></td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d3">SERVICE<br/>D'ASSIETTE DES IMPOTS</td>
                            <td rowspan="2" class="tb0r0d1"></td>
                            <td></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" class="tb0r0d4">MOIS</td>
                            <td colspan="2" class="tb0r0d4">TRIM</td>
                            <td colspan="2" class="tb0r0d4">ANNEE</td>
                            <td class="tb0r0d5"><span t-field="user.company_id.impot_service"/></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <p class="title"><strong>Determination de la base imposable</strong></p>
                <p class="title"><strong>01 – EFFECTIF DES SALARIES</strong></p>
                <div class="d0">
                    <table class="t0">
                        <tr class="t0r0">
                            <td rowspan="2" class="t0d0">CATEGORIE</td>
                            <td  rowspan="2" class="t0d0">EFFECTIF</td>
                            <td rowspan="7" class="t0d1"></td>
                            <td colspan="3" class="t0d2">BALANCE MENUSUELLE DE L'EFFECTIF</td>
                            <td rowspan="7" class="t0d1"></td>
                            <td colspan="3" class="t0d2">BALANCE ANNUELLE DE L'EFFECTIF <sup>(2)</sup></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t0d3">ENTREE</td>
                            <td class="t0d3">SORTIE</td>
                            <td class="t0d3">DIFFERENCE <sup>(1)</sup></td>
                            <td class="t0d3">ENTREE</td>
                            <td class="t0d3">SORTIE</td>
                            <td class="t0d3">DIFFERENCE <sup>(1)</sup></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr t-foreach="data['effectifs']" t-as="category">
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['categorie']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['nombre']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['mens_in']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['mens_out']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="abs(category['mens_in'] - category['mens_out'])"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['ann_in']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="category['ann_out']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="abs(category['ann_in'] - category['ann_out'])"/></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t0d4">TOTAL</td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="data['total_effectifs']['total_emp']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="data['total_effectifs']['total_mens_in']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="data['total_effectifs']['total_mens_out']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="abs(data['total_effectifs']['total_mens_in'] - data['total_effectifs']['total_mens_out'])"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="data['total_effectifs']['total_an_in']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="data['total_effectifs']['total_an_out']"/></td>
                            <td class="t0d4"><span t-esc="abs(data['total_effectifs']['total_an_in'] - data['total_effectifs']['total_an_out'])"/></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <p class="title"><strong>02 – DETERMINATION DES TAXES</strong></p>
                <div class="d1">
                    <table class="t1">
                        <tr class="t1r0">
                            <td class="t1r0d0">NATURE DES TAXES</td>
                            <td class="t1r0d0">REMUNATIONS BRUTES TOTALES</td>
                            <td class="t1r0d1">TAUX</td>
                            <td class="t1r0d2">MONTANT A PAYER</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="t1r1">
                            <td class="t1r1d0">2.1- TAXE D'APPRENTISSAGE (TA)</td>
                            <td class="t1r1d1" ><span t-esc="format_amount(data['brut'])"/></td>
                            <td class="t1r0d2" ><span t-field="user.company_id.taux_fdfp"/> %</td>
                            <td class="t1r1d3" ><span t-esc="format_amount(int(data['brut'] * user.company_id.taux_fdfp / 100))"/></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="t1r1">
                            <td class="t1r1d0">2.2- TAXE A LA FORMATION CONTINUE (TFC)</td>
                            <td class="t1r1d1" ><span t-esc="format_amount(data['brut'])"/></td>
                            <td class="t1r0d2" ><span t-field="user.company_id.taux_fdfp_fc"/> %</td>
                            <td class="t1r1d3" ><span t-esc="format_amount(int(data['brut'] * user.company_id.taux_fdfp_fc / 100))" /></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <div class="d2">
                    <table class="t2">
                        <tr class="t2r0">
                            <td class="t2r0d0">2.3- Montant cumulé de la TFC conservée depuis le début de l’année<sup>(3)</sup></td>
                            <td class="t2r0d1"></td>
                            <td class="t2r0d2"></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
                <p class="title"><strong>03 – REGULARISATION ANNUELLE <sup>(2)</sup></strong></p>
                <div class="d3">
                    <table class="t3" width="100%">
                        <tr class="t3r0">
                            <td class="t3r0d"></td>
                            <td class="t3r0d0">MONTANT</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d1">3.1– Masse salariale annuelle......................................................</td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2 t3r0d4"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d1 t3r0d3">3.2 - Montant annuel de la TFC (3.1 x 1,2 %)...................................</td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d1 t3r0d3">3.3 - Montant total de la TFC payée au cours de l’année (2.3)......</td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d1 t3r0d3">3.4 - Engagement sur plans agréés par le FDFP (utilisation directe).....</td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2 t3r0d4"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d1 t3r0d3"><div>3.5- Versement à effectuer si |3.2| est supérieur à |3.3| + |3.4|............</div>
                                <div align="center">|3.5| = |3.2| – (|3.3| + |3.4|)</div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <!--<tr>-->
                            <!--<td class="t3r0d5"></td>-->
                        <!--</tr>-->
                        <tr>
                            <td class="t3r0d6">Montant à payer</td>
                            <td class="t3r0d2"><span t-esc="format_amount(int(data['brut'] * user.company_id.taux_fdfp_fc / 100))" /></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <p class="footer">(1) - Faire précéder le chiffre par le signe (-) ou (+).<br/>
                    (2) - Rubriques à servir pour la déclaration du mois de décembre ou en cas de cessation d’activité de l’entreprise.<br/>
                    (3) - Le montant cumulé de la TFC (0,6 %) sur 12 mois est à reverser en fin d’année, si l’entreprise n’a pas bénéficié de
                    plan de formation agréé par le FDFP.<br/>
                    (4) - Les montants à payer (TA et TFC), doivent faire l’objet de deux chèques libellés respectivement à l’ordre du
                    Receveur des Impôts FDFP/TA et du Receveur des Impôts FDFP/TFC. En cas de formation agréée, joindre les pièces
                    justificatives (agrément). Aucune compensation sur les taxes FDFP n’est admise.
                </p>


            </div>
        </t>
    </t>
</template>
</data>
</odoo>